# Salesforce Script Conventions

- Always save anonymous Apex scripts in `scripts/apex/` with a `.apex` extension.
- Always save SOQL queries in `scripts/soql/` with a `.soql` extension.

## Examples

```
✅ scripts/apex/loadMessages.apex
✅ scripts/soql/getCountdownMessages.soql

❌ scripts/loadMessages.apex
❌ queries/getCountdownMessages.soql
```
